>> source: Magnolia

Beat 1/2 cup (1 stick) softened @unsalted butter{1/2%cup} for ~{2%minutes} on medium.

beat in 1/2 cup @confectioners' sugar{1/2%cup}.

Beat in 1 Tbsp @heavy cream{1%Tbsp} and 1/2 tsp @peppermint extract{1/2%tsp}.

Gradually beat in 1.5 cups additional @confectioners' sugar{1.5%cups}.

Beat ~{5%minutes}, scraping bowl occasionally.
